        srcset="https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/Elliot-Maffei_1923FEA_OBGYN_NY-Mag-Columbia-Doc1850-toned.jpg?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=550&amp;q=75&amp;w=400&amp;s=c5eeff24f27f941d92003c8e3664262c 400w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/Elliot-Maffei_1923FEA_OBGYN_NY-Mag-Columbia-Doc1850-toned.jpg?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=1100&amp;q=75&amp;w=800&amp;s=7c38b1ceda9b3e25e12e07e52fdc14db 800w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/Elliot-Maffei_1923FEA_OBGYN_NY-Mag-Columbia-Doc1850-toned.jpg?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=1649&amp;q=75&amp;w=1200&amp;s=a58e87f1813f943316b36d3932ce6cbf 1200w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/Elliot-Maffei_1923FEA_OBGYN_NY-Mag-Columbia-Doc1850-toned.jpg?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=1787&amp;q=75&amp;w=1300&amp;s=921165d29c6fb7f94332021c4fa56362 1300w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/Elliot-Maffei_1923FEA_OBGYN_NY-Mag-Columbia-Doc1850-toned.jpg?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=1993&amp;q=75&amp;w=1450&amp;s=79729f141a2e333ac0e51df6a0cd6e64 1450w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/Elliot-Maffei_1923FEA_OBGYN_NY-Mag-Columbia-Doc1850-toned.jpg?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=2199&amp;q=75&amp;w=1600&amp;s=c1596e15c100354855b168fe3cdb9b7a 1600w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/Elliot-Maffei_1923FEA_OBGYN_NY-Mag-Columbia-Doc1850-toned.jpg?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=2749&amp;q=75&amp;w=2000&amp;s=a1d2e3278a89d8fc4f2606be8b0afeb1 2000w"
                    />
                    <div class="quote__container">

          <div class="quote">
                  <h4>“I feel like I was targeted because of my situation — him knowing it was my first visit and that I was queer.”
                  </h4>
                  <h3>Elliot Maffei</h3>
                  <p>Patient: 2009</p>
                </div>
              </div>
        </figure>
      </div>

