                    />

                    <div class="quote__container">

          <div class="quote">
                  <h4>“It’s emotional abuse, as well as sexual abuse, when your predator is not scary or seemingly dangerous because your guard is down. You squash your instincts.”
                  </h4>
                  <h3>Tobi Pilavin-Weinstein</h3>
                  <p>Patient: 1992 to 1994</p>
                </div>
