    <div class="story-card__description">
                
        <h3 class="story-card__hed" >
            <a href="https://www.propublica.org/article/five-documents-helped-us-understand-how-columbia-protected-a-predator">
                                    5 Documents That Helped Us Understand How Columbia Protected a Predator
                            </a>
        </h3>

        <p class="story-card__dek" >
                            For decades, Columbia obstetrician Robert Hadden was abusing patients. Here’s some of the evidence ProPublica reporter Bianca Fortis used to investigate how the university allowed it to happen.
                    </p>

        <p class="story-card__byline">
            by <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/bianca-fortis">Bianca Fortis</a>,             <time class="timestamp" datetime="2023-09-20EDT05:00">Sept. 20, 5 a.m. EDT</time>
        </p>

            </div>
</div>
                    


        
                    
<div class="story-card story-card--standard">
    
    

                    
                    
    
        <div class="lead-art">
            <a class="aspect-3-2" href="https://www.propublica.org/article/mississippi-courts-wont-say-how-they-provide-lawyers-for-poor-clients">
                <img
                    alt=""
                    src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=utf-8,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%27http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%27%20width%3D%273%27%20height%3D%272%27%20style%3D%27background%3Atransparent%27%2F%3E"
